---
layout: base.njk
title: Kontakt
---
<section class="contact-page">
  <h1>Kontakt</h1>
  <p>Vill du boka en fotograf, köpa ett print eller bara säga hej?</p>
  <form name="kontakt" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="contact-form">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="kontakt">
    <label>Namn<input type="text" name="name" required></label>
    <label>E-post<input type="email" name="email" required></label>
    <label>Meddelande<textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea></label>
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Skicka</button>
  </form>
</section>
